## VARIABLES DE CONFIGURACI√ìN

Para facilitar ajustes globales, define estas variables CSS:

```css
:root {
  /* Duraciones */
  --anim-pulse-duration: 2s;
  --anim-flicker-duration: 3s;
  --anim-sway-duration: 4s;
  --anim-float-duration-min: 25s;
  --anim-float-duration-max: 35s;
  
  /* Intensidades */
  --anim-pulse-scale: 1.05;
  --anim-sway-angle: 3deg;
  --anim-flicker-opacity-min: 0.7;
  
  /* Timings */
  --timing-ease: ease-in-out;
  --timing-ease-out: ease-out;
  
  /* Transiciones de interacci√≥n */
  --transition-hover: 0.3s ease-out;
  --transition-expand: 0.4s ease-in-out;
}
```

**Uso:**
```css
